rows.label: bf08090100_0010
rows.name:
What's happening...
Was this your doing?

rows.label: bf08090100_0020
rows.name: You'll be alright now.

rows.label: bf08090100_0030
rows.name: The healing isn't perfect, so don't expect miracles.

rows.label: bf08090100_0040
rows.name: Hikari...

rows.label: bf08090100_0050
rows.name: So you still remember my name.

rows.label: bf08090100_0060
rows.name:
Makes sense.
You never returned to your core crystal, did you?

rows.label: bf08090100_0070
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf08090100_0080
rows.name: Better thank your good luck.

rows.label: bf08090100_0090
rows.name:
Do you have any idea how many people died
because of what Iira did?

rows.label: bf08090100_0100
rows.name:
If Meleph-sama were here
You would...

rows.label: bf08090100_0110
rows.name: Hikari... Didn't you and Shin...?

rows.label: bf08090100_0120
rows.name:
Yes.
We once fought side by side against Metsu.

rows.label: bf08090100_0130
rows.name: That's why I need to understand.

rows.label: bf08090100_0140
rows.name:
Why?
Why did you join Metsu's side?

rows.label: bf08090100_0150
rows.name: What good would knowing do?

rows.label: bf08090100_0160
rows.name: It will only make you lose faith in humanity too.

rows.label: bf08090100_0170
rows.name: I can guess.

rows.label: bf08090100_0180
rows.name:
That's why I can say
I wouldn't reach the same conclusion as you.

rows.label: bf08090100_0190
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf08090100_0200
rows.name:
Laura...
She's in there, isn't she?

rows.label: bf08090100_0210
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf08090100_0220
rows.name:
With everything you've done,
we can't forgive you.

rows.label: bf08090100_0230
rows.name: If you try to stop us again,

rows.label: bf08090100_0235
rows.name:
if you're still set on destroying the world,
we won't hold back.

rows.label: bf08090100_0240
rows.name: But, right now...

rows.label: bf08090100_0250
rows.name: That's wise.

rows.label: bf08090100_0260
rows.name:
This is the Land of Mors. A place that could be 
called a demon realm beyond our imagination.

rows.label: bf08090100_0270
rows.name: You know about this place?

rows.label: bf08090100_0280
rows.name: This land was destroyed long before Alst ever existed.

rows.label: bf08090100_0290
rows.name: The birthplace of God.

rows.label: bf08090100_0300
rows.name: That's what Metsu said.

rows.label: bf08090100_0310
rows.name: This is...God's...

rows.label: bf08090100_0320
rows.name: Shin...

rows.label: bf08090100_0330
rows.name: I know you won't change your mind easily.

rows.label: bf08090100_0340
rows.name: But hear me out.

rows.label: bf08090100_0350
rows.name: We find our friends and climb the World Tree together.

rows.label: bf08090100_0360
rows.name: Call it a ceasefire until then, okay?

rows.label: bf08090100_0370
rows.name: Working together, huh?

rows.label: bf08090100_0375
rows.name: Fine...

rows.label: bf08090100_0380
rows.name: I'm in no condition to fight you now anyway.
